Upalert is designed to help traders monitor their positions on the GMX perpetual DEX in real-time and receive alerts when certain conditions are met. For example, traders can set alerts to notify them when their positions reach certain profit or loss levels, or when the market moves in a certain direction. This can help traders make more informed decisions about when to enter or exit positions and manage their risk more effectively.

